    "For n in-domain sentences, there are n × (n -1)/2 possible combinations.",
    "Using all possible combinations would not lead to performance improvement.",
    "Therefore, the right sampling strategy helps the model to achieve performance improvement and decrease an excessive computational overhead.",
    "In the next step, the bi-encoder is trained on this training dataset (STS Benchmark and In-Domain Labeled dataset).",
    "This trained model was called Augmented SBERT (AugSBERT) (Thakur et al., 2020)."
  ],
